<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media -- Advertising:
   Next Season's Prices for TV Ads
   Slide in Reversal of Long Trends
   ----
   By Joanne Lipman
</HL>
<DATE>
05/28/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
<CO>
   CBS CCB GE NWS PEP
